title: 2003–04 Liechtenstein Cup
text: The 2003–04 <a href="Liechtenstein%20Football%20Cup">Liechtenstein Cup</a> was the fifty-ninth season of <a href="Liechtenstein">Liechtenstein</a>'s annual cup competition. Seven clubs competed with a total of sixteen teams for one spot in the <a href="2004%E2%80%9305%20UEFA%20Cup%23First%20qualifying%20round">first qualifying round</a> of the UEFA Cup. Defending champions were <a href="FC%20Vaduz">FC Vaduz</a>, who have won the cup continuously since 1998.
